Lehman’s $200 Million Suit Against Bethany ‘Ready for Trial,’ Judge Says

-- B y   L i n d a   S a n d l e r
-- 
2011-08-05T19:43:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-05/lehman-s-200-million-suit-against-bethany-ready-for-trial-judge-says.html
Lehman Brothers Holdings Inc. (LEHMQ) ’s $200
million lawsuit against Bethany Holdings Group LLC and Terry
Knutson “is ready for trial,” a judge said.  The federal court judge said in a court filing today that
he sided with Lehman, which is trying to recover on guarantees
given for loans made to buy Arizona apartments, in denying a
jury to Bethany.  To contact the reporter on this story:
